really know us

00:53.000 --> 00:55.033
as well as we
think they do?

00:55.033 --> 00:58.233
Or is the truth that we hide
more than we'd like to admit;

00:58.233 --> 01:00.033
that there are some
parts of ourselves

01:00.033 --> 01:02.000
